{{> header title="Proof of Ownership Required"}}

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>Thank you for filing a claim for the found item. To protect the security of our users and ensure items are returned to their rightful owners, we require additional <strong>proof of ownership</strong>.</p>

<p>Please upload one or more of the following documents to support your claim:</p>

<div class="info-card">
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Government-issued ID</strong> (Passport, Driver's License)</li>
    <li><strong>Purchase Receipt</strong> or invoice for the item</li>
    <li><strong>Original Photos</strong> of you with the item</li>
    <li><strong>Unique Features</strong> description (serial numbers, specific marks)</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>You can securely upload these documents through our platform by clicking the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{clientUrl}}/claims/{{claimId}}/proof" class="button">Upload Proof Documents</a>
</div>

<p>Once you've uploaded the documents, our staff will review them and update your claim status. You'll receive another email once the review is complete.</p>

